%N A197590 Decimal expansion of least x>0 satisfying f(x)=m/2, where m is the maximal value of f(x)=(cos(x))^2+(sin(3x))^2.
%C A197590 For a discussion and guide to related sequences, see A197739.
%e A197590 0.81428544842054341525317686676548785153377347...
%t A197590 (See the program at A197739.)
%o A197590 (PARI) my(t=solve(x=-0.5,-0.46875,2*cos(x)*-sin(x)+2*sin(3*x)*3*cos(3*x))); my(m=cos(t)^2+sin(3*t)^2); solve(x=.8,.9,cos(x)^2+sin(3*x)^2-m/2) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, May 17 2026
